Support maintenance, certification and enhancement of Accenture’s data privacy management system and associated governance tasks in alignment with Policy & Governance lead;
Maintain, further develop and execute strategy for external relations in data privacy, in alignment with our Government Relations team; work with selected regulators and industry bodies representing Accenture at meetings and through papers; keep abreast of technology trends and developments and their impact, develop guidance and thought leadership for internal and external audiences;
